bio: Hello, I`m Kenneth, 22, from Philippines. I am a college student, major in Biology. During free time, I usually spend it to do crypto works - for 3 years now.
contributionDescription: My contributions to Optimism doesn`t really revolve around on-chain activities, but more on being an active member of the community, and helping OP to be introduced to the new members of Optimism network. I help spread news about OP, governance news, community activities, and all things OP.

contributionLinks.description: Post that include my votes in the OP governance.

impactDescription: Participating on the Optimism governance, I think It`s important to be an active voter to help the Optimism foundation decide on how the network should go as a decentralized network. It is a chance for every member to submit what they think is the best decision for the whole network.
